# Per-run render + diff artifacts produced by FigmaParityComparator.
__Output__/

# Figma reference exports are LOCAL-ONLY (heavy binaries, go stale).
# Export them from Figma into FigmaParityReferences/ to run the checks;
# tests SKIP (not fail) when a reference is absent. See that dir's README.
FigmaParityReferences/*.png

# …except the hermetic self-test reference: not a Figma export, but a small
# PNG rendered by the harness itself from a test-only fixture view. Committing
# it keeps the comparator exercised on every CI run. See FigmaParitySelfTests.
!FigmaParityReferences/selftest-fixture.png
